{"tid":1923582,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《隱形客》刀仔鋸大樹 環球電影落實開拍新版德古拉伯爵","createTime":"2020-03-13T07:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T10:24:35.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"059f4b1dec30606a4d9f14424c6df899e1d1d0e6","tid":1923582,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:00:15.000Z","msg":"隨著700萬美元(約5,460萬港元)的低成本電影《隱形客》(The Invisible Man)全球大收超過1億美元，環球電影終於落實開拍新版吸血殭屍德古拉伯爵。不過德古拉並非大型製作，只以獨立形式上映。電影由影后妮歌潔曼舊作《毀滅者》(Destroyer)導演嘉倫古莎瑪(Karyn Kusama)執導，故事背景是現代。另外，環球正與恐怖片大師溫子仁合作推出怪物片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%E5%BE%B7%E5%8F%A4%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%E7%88%B5%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A6%E9%96%8B%E6%8B%8D-210914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%258F%25A4%25E6%258B%2589%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E7%2588%25B5%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%258B%258D-210914&d=Tw47yvsTxhso6q9O6ySnCW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=697a0c41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%E5%BE%B7%E5%8F%A4%E6%8B%89%E4%BC%AF%E7%88%B5%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A6%E9%96%8B%E6%8B%8D-210914</a>"},{"pid":"3036f7f7b76ccdd008239a318ca9c32857ce6f8e","tid":1923582,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T07:07:04.000Z","msg":"又拍？！"},{"pid":"6965a45f565bc250124b33bb76e3c4a0cb0a5b1d","tid":1923582,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"700萬美金收1億美金?<br />\n<br />\n嘩~連登仔明明踩得好勁吓架"},{"pid":"820217f5cfae5738188f19e7e111d5e85d786f2a","tid":1923582,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6965a45f565bc250124b33bb76e3c4a0cb0a5b1d","tid":1923582,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"700萬美金收1億美金?<br />\n<br />\n嘩~連登仔明明踩得好勁吓架"},"cited